discord.customcommands.permcom.syntax.er: Usage: !permcom [command] [permission] - Either 0 which is everyone or 1 is administrators.
discord.customcommands.permcom.success: Permission for command !$1 has been set to permission $2
discord.customcommands.coolcom.removed: Cooldown for command !$1 has been removed.
discord.customcommands.coolcom.success: Cooldown for command !$1 has been set to $2 seconds.
discord.customcommands.channelcom.usage: Usage: !channelcom [command] [channel / --global / --list] - Separate the channels with commas (no spaces) for multiple.
discord.customcommands.channelcom.global: Command !$1 will now work in every channel.
discord.customcommands.channelcom.succes: Command !$1 will now only work in channel(s): $2.
discord.customcommands.channelcom.404: No channels are set on that command.
discord.customcommands.pricecom.success: Cost for command !$1 has been set to $2.
discord.customcommands.customapijson.err: !$1: An error occurred processing the API.
